
Frequently Asked Questions

Q. Where can I get help for dc++ itself?
A. DC++ faq is available in your program's help and here:
	http://www.dslreports.com/faq/dc
   The DC++ answers are available here:
	https://answers.launchpad.net/dcplusplus

Q. Where can I get updates to my dc++ client?
A. Updates can be gotten here:
	http://dcplusplus.sourceforge.net/

Q. I don't get any results when searching, and/or can't download from other users. Why?
A. This has something to do with the settings within your client. Follow the link below.
        http://www.dslreports.com/faq/6524

Q. Where can I get more information about Verlihub?
A. The verlihub homepage is here:
	http://verlihub-project.org/
   Support hub is here:
	dchub://hub.verlihub.net:7777/

Anything not covered above should be asked in main chat.
